productReviews.reviewText: I tried to cremate it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
My co-worker Erick has one of these. He says it looks fluffy.
My co-worker Aurthur has one of these. He says it looks white.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
